{"tid":1767164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實依家D黑社會係咪小丑黎？","createTime":"2019-12-03T06:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T06:23:53.000Z","uid":75636,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d2e480e20d572f95840c848077efb29dfc38ba0","tid":1767164,"uid":75636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"九十年代d黑社會成日話12點後佢話事，<br />\n咩紅色專線小巴佢睇，的士又睇。好似好撚架勢咁。<br />\n但呢幾年只係淪為黑警打手，做condom。<br />\n當日一班燒黃紙兄弟，拜曬關公，誓誓旦旦要隊冧班狗，點知依家一個二個做曬黑警既自私雞。<br />\n由以前既逗龜，變成Good Morning Sir , Good Bye Sir，真係仲乖過狗仔。<br />\n好心你地班黑社會收檔啦，老啦返歸耕田養老，咪走出黎獻世。<br />\n<br />\n如果你身邊仲有人自稱黑社會既，麻煩邀請佢地去紅館開棟篤笑，因為佢地班小丑真係好好笑啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2835186af2c250062b35184526234e36af73d788","tid":1767164,"uid":52804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695ec6c3532d158da5a03314dae16d70e1f4783a","tid":1767164,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efaa67ed357527cb184fdfe076b4baa00c6c7789","tid":1767164,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"黑社會 = 警甴梯隊"},{"pid":"44a4aa57ca5d01bbaae166b1346fc4004a25ef0a","tid":1767164,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04149e679fae467e74c15ae8b1dcb15265e25000","tid":1767164,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"到人地打人，你又驚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\